{
  "stem": "27507.8",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We were kind of a pretty basic hiding place in the flat where we lived then in this-- in the [POLISH] flat opposite the factory, and all squashed into this very narrow space, maybe something like two meter one way and half a meter the other way, covered with plywood, and practically with no possibility to breathe even.",
      "word_count": 58
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I was almost suffocating there, because I was sitting on the side, and somehow managing to breath, but hardly.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And we spent-- and then 10:00 o'clock passed.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And then Germans promised that they are going to search everything, search the flats.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And if anybody is going to be found out, they are going to be shot on the spot.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And they would do it, of course.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "So we heard them coming.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And we heard them breaking into the flats on the first floor, and then breaking into the flats on the second floor.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And if they would come into our flat, a very good likelihood that they would find us, because it was too primitive as a hiding place.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "But, finally, they went into the second floor.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "But they didn't come to the floor-- to our floor.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "It was already enough for them of work for this morning.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And they went somewhere else.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we were saved once again.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we stayed there still quite some time, until in the evening we crawled out.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we cooked some potatoes, something to eat.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we stayed the night in the flat.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But hardly anybody slept.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we didn't know what was going to happen.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We didn't know if people were-- if the Jews were going to come back.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Or maybe they would take them all from [POLISH] Street, and take them God knows where.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
